data.description:
Move in with instant equity! This immaculate 2bed 3 bath townhome feels luxurious and spacious.
 The large front porch is great for morning coffee while enjoying beautiful mountain views.  
The open floor plan you've been desiring is finally here, with tons of windows for morning and afternoon sun. The living room flows perfectly into the dining room which looks into the backyard and is next to the beautifully upgraded kitchen- perfect for entertaining friends and family. Upstairs you have a separate area for kids to play or a nice reading nook in the open loft. You'll love the Master Bedroom and yes, more mountain views! This bedroom has a   walk-in closet. A bathroom with an updated vanity and a spa-like shower with built in seating. The second bedroom is spacious with an east facing window. A third bathroom completes the upstairs. 
Features of this home includes; Granite countertops & Stainless-Steel Appliances, Upgraded Lighting Throughout the Entire Home, and a Private Backyard. Seller just installed a new radon system. This townhome is an end unit that is adjacent to open greenspace with tons of great trails nearby. This community has 3 great parks, endless trails and a wonderful dog park.
